title: DDFP 271: The best QB-WR duos & CJ2K
itunes:title: DDFP 271: The best QB-WR duos & CJ2K
description:
Shek & Handsome Hank attempt to call the Bengals' Hue Jackson's bluff by taking it upon themselves to name ten quarterback-wide receiver duos better than Andy Dalton and A.J. Green. Can they accomplish this tall task? Plus, Shek speaks with New York Jets running back Chris Johnson about new teammates Eric Decker and Michael Vick, head coach Rex Ryan and the NFL's fastest player.
